OL,3,CMan guilty of murder after callously
OL,4,Cdisposing woman's body in his shed
OL,6,FA man who killed a woman and disposed
OL,7,Fof her body in his garden shed has
OL,8,Fbeen found guilty of murder.
OL,10,FChristopher Barlow, 62, initially told
OL,11,Fthe court that the woman, Mariann
OL,12,FBorocz, 55, had never been in his
OL,13,Fhouse and he had no idea how her body
OL,14,Fhad ended up in his shed.
