OL,3,CMan guilty of murder after callously
OL,4,Cdisposing woman's body in his shed
OL,6,FThe last sighting of Ms Borocz was at
OL,7,F9:30am on 14 December, 2024, when she
OL,8,Fwas seen with Barlow, turning into
OL,9,FPedder Street where he lives, a court
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FPolice later trawled local CCTV which
OL,13,Flead them to Barlow, who lied about
OL,14,Fhis encounter with Ms Borocz when
OL,15,Fpolice questioned him at his house.
OL,17,FBarlow was arrested on 23 December
OL,18,F2024, and Ms Borocz's body was later
OL,19,Ffound in his shed, nine days after she
OL,20,Fwas reported missing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
