OL,3,CMan guilty of murder after callously
OL,4,Cdisposing woman's body in his shed
OL,6,FRebecca Macaulay-Addison, Specialist
OL,7,FProsecutor for CPS North West's
OL,8,FComplex Casework Unit, said:
OL,9,F"Christopher Barlow killed Mariann
OL,10,FBorocz and stripped her of her
OL,11,Fclothes, before callously disposing of
OL,12,Fher body in his shed.
OL,14,F"He took steps to prevent Ms Borocz's
OL,15,Fbody being found at his address by
OL,16,Flying to his friend and cancelling his
OL,17,Fcleaner so neither would attend his
OL,18,Fhouse.
